{"tid":188782,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"六月蘇格蘭","createTime":"2017-04-06T02:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T21:32:45.000Z","uid":103815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0eb67381afeb082ddbe080d68e8f541ac0389d07","tid":188782,"uid":103815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:53:37.000Z","msg":"自膠第一次出post放左係吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放返係旅遊台先<br />\n<br />\n小弟諗住六月去曼睇完卡膠之後直上蘇格蘭玩5日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見好多Ching推介Isle of Skye<br />\n有冇巴打可以分享下報過既local tour, 尼斯湖係咪可skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外Edinburgh用一兩日係咪已經夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想放多啲時間係近郊, 上網啲相好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求巴打絲打𧶽教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0eee56a5153a86ad6ec927ba6fdd0544693cfe","tid":188782,"uid":48211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T02:55:54.000Z","msg":"嚟緊六月中近尾去Edinburgh玩幾日 <br />\n巴打幾時去？<br />\n我諗住報local tour<br />\nHea玩"},{"pid":"dfd27b0f79195a48c03adbdc23d6515e5b983527","tid":188782,"uid":103815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T03:05:30.000Z","msg":"我六月頭去<br />\n見MacBackpackers多後生仔報<br />\n諗住報個3 Day Tour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a50ab04747b90119b0253f9bafe6cd016ebe26f","tid":188782,"uid":103815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T06:54:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d79adec5b5636670723aaab05898059f8cd119","tid":188782,"uid":48211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T10:31:20.000Z","msg":"巴打求包膠有咩玩<br />\n三日tour睇過好似150磅左右<br />\n我都係報一日係city行下算"},{"pid":"23641b50ad1ab29a7a67679a0c25b6f8be39115a","tid":188782,"uid":103815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:15:02.000Z","msg":"Highland係蘇格蘭精髓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試下google打skye<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEdinburgh聽講兩日是基本 我仲揾緊資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2958ba5cf3ef12262b0208db25b324ead5f7c1b","tid":188782,"uid":102606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T09:00:18.000Z","msg":"Edinburgh 快玩應該兩日都可以嘅，前年玩左3日但覺得可以留多日<br />\n<br />\n之後喺inverness報左highland experience嘅 isle of skye one day tour, 佢帶我哋去Elgol, 個景係靚嘅，但完全冇去portree同再北啲，覺得路線唔夠好，同埋架車好似最滿可以裝30人，覺得太多，應該揀少人嘅啲。<br />\n<br />\n尼斯湖係冇特別嘅，不過通常都會經過，唔駛揀個特別feature佢嘅tour"},{"pid":"4debf50bfe4ca425b5b3bffbd118c2cc46346bfe","tid":188782,"uid":72502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:39:00.000Z","msg":"我都係六月去蘇格蘭，我報埋團啦。<br />\n3日Total:$183 GBP 連住宿"},{"pid":"6cb4f9995b898f2b8176ec447979c9319534baf9","tid":188782,"uid":72502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:39:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我六月頭去<br />\n見MacBackpackers多後生仔報<br />\n諗住報個3 Day Tour<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係報呢個"},{"pid":"a633b28323b95fabaaf3b51d41860e3d618a9310","tid":188782,"uid":95408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:52:19.000Z","msg":"黎緊八月去 留名學野 時間緊迫我應該得四日fullday 一日市內再join個三日團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但仲未睇得岩 諗緊hp果架火車值唔值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8feb66ae87f2f6557c10e21c90fafc5367aa18","tid":188782,"uid":538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊八月去 留名學野 時間緊迫我應該得四日fullday 一日市內再join個三日團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但仲未睇得岩 諗緊hp果架火車值唔值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭過HP火車  要提前上網買飛<br />\nWalk in唔會有飛買到<br />\n好多人會霸窗位影條橋<br />\n舊年影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zXKS7i6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzXKS7i6.jpg&h=a78f6585&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acb449a0a11452ff54d287ebb0b2133848f31335","tid":188782,"uid":538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T17:28:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自膠第一次出post放左係吹水台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 放返係旅遊台先<br />\n<br />\n小弟諗住六月去曼睇完卡膠之後直上蘇格蘭玩5日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見好多Ching推介Isle of Skye<br />\n有冇巴打可以分享下報過既local tour, 尼斯湖係咪可skip<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外Edinburgh用一兩日係咪已經夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想放多啲時間係近郊, 上網啲相好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求巴打絲打𧶽教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nEdinburgh 2日行景點同hea 咩都夠<br />\n通常local tour點都會經過loch ness 俾你影一影<br />\n其實Isle of skye三日都夠 <br />\n雖然我係報左rabbies 5天團去埋Ullapool 個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3922988af89dceca5f42484779ce8e44534c5701","tid":188782,"uid":95408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊八月去 留名學野 時間緊迫我應該得四日fullday 一日市內再join個三日團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但仲未睇得岩 諗緊hp果架火車值唔值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭過HP火車  要提前上網買飛<br />\nWalk in唔會有飛買到<br />\n好多人會霸窗位影