\"hkgmoji\" />  macbackpackers 幾號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3820bebf09a6c7b75f27f2648a4e3934cc634515","tid":188782,"uid":103815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T15:18:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黎緊八月去 留名學野 時間緊迫我應該得四日fullday 一日市內再join個三日團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但仲未睇得岩 諗緊hp果架火車值唔值得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搭過HP火車  要提前上網買飛<br />\nWalk in唔會有飛買到<br />\n好多人會霸窗位影條橋<br />\n舊年影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zXKS7i6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzXKS7i6.jpg&h=a78f6585&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>唔係呀我諗住join果啲包埋去hp火車嘅tour呀 果啲應該會幫我地買定飛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你要問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n坐車影反而無咁靚 sample相係咪要自駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  時間緊逼 留返下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684a17d2464301cabec34dacfa2ef6a301c8ba74","tid":188782,"uid":30528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"之前去過7日 三日係愛丁堡 今日上咗去Loch lomond 一日係Glasgow <br />\n愛丁堡建議留三日 你一定會愛上呢個城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上Loch Lomond行山 啲境好靚 <br />\n個度唔算係遊客區 啲local會撩我地傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而Glasgow就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15048e522da8fc7fa5f42eaf4717c814b305c5c","tid":188782,"uid":30528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前去過7日 三日係愛丁堡 <span style=\"color: red;\">三</span>日上咗去Loch lomond 一日係Glasgow <br />\n愛丁堡建議留三日 你一定會愛上呢個城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上Loch Lomond行山 啲境好靚 <br />\n個度唔算係遊客區 啲local會撩我地傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而Glasgow就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"10c9da9cb76041ce8a3bd88180349f49e944439e","tid":188782,"uid":17052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T22:30:35.000Z","msg":"我都想6月去 留個名先"},{"pid":"7f2ff273540254cd6f6d64c1882a74db953bb239","tid":188782,"uid":77702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T22:52:49.000Z","msg":"係愛丁堡住，有咩可以問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c271fa62244447fe1d64e81d92109f5591bb94d","tid":188782,"uid":103815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上年8月去 留左十日係Scotland 8月有得睇Fringe Festival真係好熱鬧好開心 參加左macbackpackers 3日團 大家都好玩得又可以一齊行山 雖然天氣好飄忽一時好猛太陽一時又落下雨咁 不過整體都幾好 幾適合後生既去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己一個報左macbackpackers 希望有人一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nscotland啲天氣好唔穩定?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c1350dff36d2703374e35891e44f9fe6e39265","tid":188782,"uid":103815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係愛丁堡住，有咩可以問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩係必食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋邊度買同睇whiskey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0b5387dd3e708800c680cca1443fdcad42cfaf","tid":188782,"uid":60997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上年8月去 留左十日係Scotland 8月有得睇Fringe Festival真係好熱鬧好開心 參加左macbackpackers 3日團 大家都好玩得又可以一齊行山 雖然天氣好飄忽一時好猛太陽一時又落下雨咁 不過整體都幾好 幾適合後生既去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己一個報左macbackpackers 希望有人一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nscotland啲天氣好唔穩定?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果陣同團有一個香港人 有台灣人 有澳洲 意大利等等 都玩得埋<br />\n<br />\n啲天氣成日都好多雲 我之後去couchsurfing個host再車左我上去睇都係好多雲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/141947_343a9de447b873581411236bb9bf2e91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F141947_343a9de447b873581411236bb9bf2e91.jpg&h=2011a3ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/106N26D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F106N26D.jpg&h=87ce7a72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8r0wH0o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8r0wH0o.jpg&h=7e3e6370&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c4f293fc2916d0a697308fdf63eaff75046c571","tid":188782,"uid":60997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係愛丁堡住，有咩可以問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩係必食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋邊度買同睇whiskey<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n近edinburgh castle有whisky廠"}]}